    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This powerhouse utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear torque curve and a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, paired with an M Variable Differential Lock that ensures optimal power distribution across the rear axle. This example has been meticulously maintained with a recent preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator refresh. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical synchronization and hydraulic steering feedback remain sharp and communicative. A pure, high-revving analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
