    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Deep Sea Mica offers a blend of sophisticated luxury and proven reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small, superficial scuff on the lower rear bumper from city parking. Inside, the Parchment leather seats are supple and free of cracks or stains, and the cabin remains a strictly smoke-free environment. All electronic features, including the heated seats, navigation system, and premium audio, operate perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented history of synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The Michelin tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently replaced. It drives smoothly with no vibrations or unusual noises. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been well-cared for and is ready for its next owner. Includes two keys and all original manuals.",
